# {{ project_name }}

## Project Structure

This is a Swift + TypeScript monorepo: SwiftUI mobile app + Hono REST API.

- `apps/ios/` — your Xcode project lives here (see README for first-time setup)
- `apps/api/` — Hono REST API with OpenAPI spec (TypeScript, pnpm)
- `packages/db/` — Prisma database schema and client
- `packages/types/` — Shared TypeScript types
- `packages/config/` — Shared TypeScript configuration

## Commands

### TypeScript (API)
- `pnpm start` — Start Postgres + API dev server (clean exit on Ctrl+C)
- `pnpm build` — Build all TS packages
- `pnpm test` — Run all TS tests (Vitest)
- `pnpm lint` — Lint with Biome
- `pnpm typecheck` — TypeScript type checking
- `pnpm db:push` — Push Prisma schema to database
- `pnpm db:studio` — Open Prisma Studio

### OpenAPI
- `pnpm --filter {{ scope }}/api openapi:export` — Export OpenAPI spec to stdout
- OpenAPI spec served live at `http://localhost:3001/api/openapi.json`

### Swift (Mobile)
- Open `apps/ios/` in Xcode (see `apps/ios/README.md` for first-time setup)
- Build and run from Xcode (Cmd+R) — code signing handled by Xcode with your Apple ID

## Development

1. `pnpm install` — Install TS dependencies
2. `pnpm db:push` — Push database schema
3. `pnpm start` — Start Postgres + API server
4. Open `apps/ios/` in Xcode and run on simulator or device

## API

- REST API serves all routes under `/api` prefix
- OpenAPI spec: `GET /api/openapi.json` (use with Swift OpenAPI Generator)
- Health check: `GET /api/health`
- User CRUD: `GET /api/users`, `POST /api/users`

## Conventions

### TypeScript (apps/api/, packages/)
- Strict TypeScript (`strict: true`)
- Biome for linting and formatting
- All packages use workspace protocol (`workspace:*`)
- Routes defined with `@hono/zod-openapi` (`createRoute` + `app.openapi()`)
- Every app and package has at least one test

### Swift (apps/ios/)
- SwiftUI for all views
- Use Swift OpenAPI Generator for the API client (see `apps/ios/README.md`)
- All API models conform to `Codable`; use `keyDecodingStrategy = .convertFromSnakeCase`
